Author: tf2manu994
Text: yup definitely see a doctor. you don't necessarily have to tell them about your ed, but it may be useful, electrolytes moderate heart rate, and a lot of people with ed have bradychardia temporarily. up to you though, you could dress it up ( "I haven't been eating a lot recently but it's just because I've been sick", "I've been throwing up a lot recently but it's just because I've been sick") if that helps you go. but definitely please go, heart problems aren't worth messing up

Text: heart problems are a really big deal, you should definitely tell someone
